---
title: Cal Smart Turkey Patties in Tikka Sauce with Cilantro Rice
description: Flecks of cilantro stems don't just make these turkey patties look pretty, they also add a ton of flavour! Tikka sauce blends beautifully with cream cheese to give this curry a velvety texture without the heaviness.
